n >65a vs 5% en <65a","guid":"mQ5ZJ_bpTrSUKSJ-1S9ldA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"Hernias encarceladas -> causa frecuente en AM (inguinal, crural)","guid":"6nAD5GWGRPeNR-hoFXFKnw","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"Ileo biliar -> casi exclusivo de AM (mujer >70a con colelitiasis)","guid":"TvPNnNWjRNWU5_uhb_Qzjw","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"28","text":"Fecaloma/impactacion fecal -> causa subestimada en AM","guid":"blZF2hP6So-Vch9zaeqiYQ","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"28","text":"Volvulo sigmoideo -> AM con megacolon, institucionalizados","guid":"9D3ocajORXeCIxTskZtJ6A","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"28","text":"Carcinomatosis peritoneal -> frecuente en AM oncologico","guid":"wHNUWPAgQra4xdqS4NSbYA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"0","text":"Etiologia por Frecuencia","guid":"uFwTgOtYT7C5s92MJvFPeg","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"INTESTINO DELGADO (80% de OI)","guid":"ZYBVQ8tCTgWtlp_A8HztQw","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Bridas y adherencias (60-75%) -> cx abdominal previa","guid":"_F81lB8qQ66sgtGrvECgrw","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Hernias (15-20%) -> inguinal, crural, incisional, interna","guid":"TZxlzUgpSt6Mku4ywSXiNQ","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Neoplasia (5-10%) -> primaria o metastasica","guid":"xkwbh5keSWivJMzHPqEPiA","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"Enfermedad de Crohn -> estenosis fibrotica","guid":"aqJUzsxFRSyaJrVGfx0-Fw","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"37","text":"Ileo biliar (1-4%) -> TRIADA DE RIGLER","guid":"kK71_uwxQomyitA06eIBeQ","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Aerobilia","guid":"BxHWQsfzRZSM7sgfcotMYg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"Calculo ectopico (ileon terminal)","guid":"U6KxRo3fSKyFlDjiDa421w","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"Distension ID","guid":"7HwcwjnbQIqPPMQ35qzikg","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"37","text":"Bezoar -> fitobezoar (diospirobezoar 